{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"15ffc96248","title":"在习仲勋关于入藏干部应做好民族工作的电报上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e8104a04c9","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":13,"articleId":"15ffc96248"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"bbc75a90b7","name":"习仲勋","type":"人物"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"b18b8d396b","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"15ffc96248","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"习仲勋，当时任中共中央西北局第二书记、西北军政委员会副主席。"},{"id":"a4d6cf8da3","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"15ffc96248","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李维汉，当时任中共中央统战部部长、中央人民政府民族事务委员会主任。刘格平，当时任中央人民政府民族事务委员会副主任。"},{"id":"84e881a9ed","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"15ffc96248","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"习仲勋1952年1月10日给毛泽东的报告中提出的意见主要是：我入藏干部应根据实际情况做好民族工作，防止过急过高要求。内地藏族聚居地区暂不进行土地改革，喇嘛寺的土地目前均以不动为好，特别是佛教寺院的土地过早征收于我不利：在游牧区也不应提“反恶霸”口号，半农半牧区也不进行土改。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7f8f318f90","type":"title","text":"在习仲勋关于人藏干部应做好民族工作的电报上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"15ffc96248"},{"id":"b18b8d396b","type":"paragraph","text":"请季维汉、刘格平以二同志商复。习仲勋同志的意见以值得注意。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"15ffc96248"},{"id":"a4d6cf8da3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"15ffc96248"},{"id":"84e881a9ed","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十三日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"15ffc96248"}],"page":{"id":"7a73817b29","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"15ffc96248","start":262,"end":262}}}},"__N_SSG":true}